\c 47
\s Amanzi aphilisayo asethempelini
\p
\v 1 Emva kwalokho wangibuyisela emnyango wendlu\x + 41.1,2.\x*, khangela-ke, amanzi aphuma ngaphansi\x + Jow. 3.18; Zek. 14.8; Isam. 22.1; Hlab. 46.4; Joha. 4.10.\x* kombundu wendlu ngasempumalanga\x + 9.3.\x*; ngoba ingaphambili yendlu yayingasempumalanga; lamanzi ehla esuka ngaphansi esuka ehlangothini lokunene lwendlu, ngaseningizimu kwelathi\x + 43.13.\x*.
\v 2 Wasengikhupha \add nge\add*ndlela yesango ngasenyakatho\x + 40.35.\x*, wangibhodisa \add nge\add*ndlela engaphandle wangisa esangweni elingaphandle, \add nge\add*ndlela ekhangele ngasempumalanga\x + 40.6.\x*. Khangela-ke, kwageleza amanzi avela ehlangothini lwesokunene.
\v 3 Ekuphumeni kwendoda\x + 40.3.\x* ngasempumalanga, elentambo esandleni sayo\x + Jer. 31.39; Zek. 1.16; Hez. 40.3; Zek. 2.1.\x*, yalinganisa izingalo eziyinkulungwane, yangidabulisa phakathi kwamanzi; amanzi afika enqagaleni.
\v 4 Walinganisa futhi inkulungwane, wangidabulisa emanzini; amanzi afika emadolweni. Walinganisa futhi inkulungwane, wangidabulisa; amanzi afika ekhalweni.
\v 5 Walinganisa futhi inkulungwane; kwaba ngumfula engingeke ngiwuchaphe, ngoba amanzi ayesephakeme, amanzi ongantsheza kuwo, umfula owawungeke wachatshwa.
\p
\v 6 Wasesithi kimi: Ubonile yini, ndodana yomuntu? Wasengihambisa, wangenza ngabuyela ekhunjini lomfula.
\v 7 Ekubuyeleni kwami, khangela-ke, ekhunjini lomfula kwakulezihlahla ezinengi kakhulu ngapha langapha\x + 47.12; Isam. 22.2.\x*.
\v 8 Wasesithi kimi: La amanzi aphumela ngaselizweni lempumalanga\x + Josh. 22.10,11; Josh. 13.2; 18.17; Jow. 3.4.\x*, ehlele enkangala, abesesiya elwandle\x + Dute. 3.17; 4.49; Josh. 3.16; 2 Kho. 14.25.\x*; athi esekhutshelwe olwandle\x + Dute. 3.17; 4.49; Josh. 3.16; 2 Kho. 14.25.\x*, amanzi azakwelatshwa.
\v 9 Kuzakuthi-ke, sonke isidalwa esiphilayo\x + Gen. 1.20.\x*, esinyakazelayo\x + Gen. 1.20,21; 7.21; 8.17; 9.7.\x*, loba ngaphi lapho imifula efika khona, sizaphila. Futhi kuzakuba khona inhlanzi ezinengi kakhulu, ngoba amanzi la azafika lapho; ngoba zizakwelatshwa; ngoba kuzaphila konke lapho umfula ofika khona.
\v 10 Kuzakuthi-ke, abagoli benhlanzi beme ngakuwo kusukela e-Engedi\x + 1 Sam. 23.29.\x* kuze kube se-Enegilayimi\x + Isa. 15.8.\x*; kuzakuba lendawo yokuchaya amambule\x + 26.5.\x*. Inhlanzi zabo zizakuba ngenhlobo zazo, njengenhlanzi zolwandle olukhulu\x + 47.15,19,20; 48.28; Josh. 15.12.\x*, ezinengi kakhulu.
\v 11 Kodwa izindawo zawo ezilodaka\x + Jobe 40.21.\x* lamaxhaphozi awo\x + Isa. 30.14.\x* kakuyikwelatshwa; kuzanikelwa ekubeni litshwayi\x + Dute. 29.23; Gen. 14.3.\x*.
\v 12 Futhi ngasemfuleni ekhunjini lwawo, ngapha langapha\x + 47.7.\x*, kuzakhula sonke isihlahla sokudla\x + Gen. 2.9.\x*, ohlamvu laso\x + Jer. 17.8.\x* kaliyikubuna\x + Jobe 14.18.\x*, lesithelo saso kasiyikuphela. Sizathela\x + Isam. 22.2.\x* isithelo saso esitsha\x + Isa. 28.4.\x* njengokwenyanga zaso, ngoba amanzi aso aphuma endaweni engcwele. Isithelo saso sizakuba yikudla, lehlamvu laso libe ngelokwelapha\x + 47.7.\x*\x + Isam. 22.2.\x*.
\s Imingcele yelizwe
\p
\v 13 Itsho njalo iNkosi uJehova: Lo uzakuba ngumngcele, elizakudla ilifa lelizwe ngawo njengokwezizwe ezilitshumi lambili zakoIsrayeli\x + 45.8.\x*. UJosefa \add uzakuba\add* lezabelo \add ezimbili\x + Gen. 48.5; Josh. 17.14,17; 1 Lan. 5.1; 48.4,5.\x*\add*.
\v 14 Njalo lizakudla ilifa lalo, omunye njengomunye, engaphakamisa isandla sami \add ngalo\add* ukulinika oyihlo\x + Gen. 12.7; 13.15; 15.7; 17.8; 26.3; 28.13.\x*. Njalo lelilizwe lizawela kini libe yilifa\x + 48.29.\x*.
\v 15 Njalo lokhu kuzakuba ngumngcele welizwe ngakuhlangothi lwenyakatho, kusukela olwandle olukhulu\x + 47.10.\x*, indlela yeHethiloni\x + 48.1.\x*, ekungeneni eZedadi\x + Nani 34.8.\x*.
\v 16 IHamathi\x + 48.1.\x*\x + Nani 34.8.\x*\x + 1 Kho. 8.65.\x*, iBerotha\x + 2 Sam. 8.8; 1 Lan. 11.39.\x*, iSibirayimi ephakathi komngcele weDamaseko\x + 48.1.\x*\x + Isa. 7.8.\x* lomngcele weHamathi\x + 1 Kho. 8.65.\x*, iHazeri-Hathikhoni esemngceleni weHawurani\x + 47.18; Jobe 30.6.\x*.
\v 17 Lomngcele osuka elwandle uzakuba yiHazari-Enoni\x + 48.1.\x*\x + Nani 34.9,10.\x*, umngcele weDamaseko\x + 48.1.\x*\x + Isa. 7.8.\x*, lenyakatho ngasenyakatho, lomngcele weHamathi\x + 48.1.\x*\x + 1 Kho. 8.65.\x*. La\add lolu\add* luhlangothi lwenyakatho.
\v 18 Futhi uhlangothi lwempumalanga lizalulinganisa lusuka phakathi kweHawurani\x + 47.18; Jobe 30.6.\x*, lusuka phakathi kweDamaseko\x + Isa. 7.8.\x*, lusuka phakathi kweGileyadi\x + Josh. 13.10.\x*, lusuka phakathi kwelizwe lakoIsrayeli \add ngase\add*Jordani, kusuke emngceleni kuze kufike elwandle olungempumalanga\x + Jow. 2.20; Zek. 14.8; Dan. 11.45.\x*. La\add lolu\add* luzakuba luhlangothi lwempumalanga.
\v 19 Lohlangothi lweningizimu ngaseningizimu\x + 48.28.\x*, kusukela\x + 48.28.\x* eTamari\x + Gen. 14.7; 2 Lan. 20.2.\x* kuze kube semanzini\x + Nani 20.13.\x* eMeribathi-Kadeshi\x + Nani 34.5.\x*, emfuleni\x + 48.28.\x* kuze kube selwandle olukhulu\x + 47.10.\x*. La\add lolu\add* luzakuba luhlangothi lweningizimu ngaseningizimu\x + Eks. 26.18,35; Hez. 20.46; Zek. 6.6; 9.14.\x*.
\v 20 Lohlangothi lwentshonalanga luzakuba lulwandle olukhulu kusukela emngceleni\x + 47.10.\x*, kuze kube maqondana lokungena eHamathi\x + 1 Kho. 8.65.\x*. Lolu luhlangothi lwentshonalanga.
\v 21 Ngokunjalo lizazehlukanisela lelilizwe njengokwezizwe zakoIsrayeli\x + 45.8.\x*.
\p
\v 22 Kuzakuthi-ke, lilabe ngenkatho\x + 45.1; 48.29.\x* libe yilifa kini, lakwabezizwe abahlala phakathi kwenu\x + Efe. 3.6.\x*, abazazala abantwana phakathi kwenu. Njalo bazakuba kini\x + Roma 10.12; Gal. 3.28; Kol. 3.11.\x* njengabazalelwe elizweni phakathi kwabantwana bakoIsrayeli\x + Eks. 12.19,48,49; Levi 16.29.\x*. Bazakudla ilifa ngenkatho kanye lani phakathi kwezizwe zakoIsrayeli\x + 45.1; 48.29.\x*.
\v 23 Kuzakuthi-ke, esizweni owezizwe ahlala njengowezizwe kiso, lapho liza\add m\add*nika ilifa lakhe, itsho iNkosi uJehova.
